ReloadFunctions
1
Open your browser and navigate to: "https://IP_Data_Collector/". You can also use
the a4conf icon on the Data Collector desktop.
2
Click the "..." icon located in the top right corner of any application section.
Made with Scribe - https://scribehow.com 2
3
Click "Reload" to reload the Data Collector configurations.
4
Click "Reload" to reload the Data Sender configurations.
Made with Scribe - https://scribehow.com 3
5
Click "Download" to download a JSON file containing the a4GATE configurations.
6
Click "Upload" to upload the application configurations from a local JSON file.
Made with Scribe - https://scribehow.com 4
7
Click "Admin" if you want to elevate yourself as admin user.
8
Insert your "admin" credentials, then click the "Login" button.
